{"tid":18783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實熱戀期係咪得一次","createTime":"2016-12-02T13:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T13:10:19.000Z","uid":20038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aba6f848ab8c1a8f3492bcfcc79543431169af8","tid":18783,"uid":20038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"第一次好認真去拍拖"},{"pid":"707066be24a00f170f8fc23f33d47159644bf544","tid":18783,"uid":20038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"出唔哂 禁錯制<br />\n第一次好認真去拍拖 拍左年半<br />\n我仲好愛對方 對佢既愛有增無減 <br />\n以前對方就算好忙都會抽空見<br />\n今日佢真係忙就會推左我 唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n仲有好多細微野會見到佢無以前咁主動<br />\n性方面都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我自己就算忙 好攰可以見一定會去見 <br />\n好驚對方離開自己<br />\n就算無做錯野 有時新鮮感先係最大敵人"},{"pid":"bad05a6bba0534326fb0343b845f2133cdbecf52","tid":18783,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"有新鮮感咪有新既熱暖期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d8c1423b153101d5fb36e24813697b9d95d0c0","tid":18783,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有新鮮感咪有新既熱戀期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}